    <div class="section">
        <h2>AI Solution Overview</h2>
        <p>
            The AI-Based Smart Water Usage Advisor helps users understand and reduce their
            daily water consumption using AI concepts such as data analysis and intelligent
            recommendations. The system studies usage patterns and provides suggestions
            to avoid wastage and promote sustainable water use.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Role of AI</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Analyzes water usage data</li>
            <li>Identifies usage patterns and wastage</li>
            <li>Generates smart recommendations</li>
            <li>Supports water conservation decisions</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Responsible AI Considerations</h2>
        <p>
            This system does not collect personal data and avoids biased decision-making.
            AI outputs are transparent, ethical, and designed only for positive
            environmental impact.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Expected Impact</h2>
        <p>
            The project helps reduce water wastage, increases awareness about sustainable
            water usage, and encourages eco-friendly habits among users.
        </p>
